      <title>受政策推动，中国债券收益率有望降至 1.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/traders-see-china-yield-fall-to-1-5-on-everything-rally-hope</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国明年将转向宽松的货币政策，这引发了人们看涨的押注，即中国主权债务收益率将从历史低点进一步下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/traders-see-china-yield-fall-to-1-5-on-everything-rally-hope</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 01:49:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
